{"tid":1978620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全部人同我開fb分身account！","createTime":"2020-04-18T22:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T04:03:07.000Z","uid":228945,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"97f9632ea3975e4a00d616b55dcb7d6e35c23852","tid":1978620,"uid":228945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T22:29:53.000Z","msg":"眼見而家藍屍陣營咁團結<br />\n當然要做返啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以開分身account 係必須！<br />\n<br />\n首先要Like晒所有出名藍page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如港人講地、今日正言、保皇黨議員<br />\n總之見到就like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住就係入藍group<br />\n一search守護香港、撐警就大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLike完page入完group要點做？<br />\n緊係要分化佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 喺藍page/group留言<br />\n當然要同個post相關<br />\n但重點係要借啲意踩返建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假設個post係講廿三條<br />\n<br />\n可以試吓留言：<br />\n<br />\n支持廿三條立法！<br />\n但系民建联同政府做咗咁多年都立唔到￼<br />\n唔知佢哋做紧乜<br />\n仲叫人九月投佢哋￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同饭民黑暴有咩分別？<br />\n唔會再俾佢哋呃到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 喺藍group開post <br />\n<br />\n可以試吓分享吓經歷：<br />\n<br />\n今日俾個蓝友自己人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼<br />\n佢话我未捐过物资俾警察<br />\n又未去过集会<br />\n唔配做蓝营嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又或者諗吓其他題材／手法<br />\n<br />\n例如話某啲藍屍太暴力<br />\n連儂牆打人的士肥佬<br />\n將軍澳斬人等等<br />\n呢啲人影響佢哋守法非暴力形象<br />\n要同佢哋割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最好夾雜吓殘體字、藍屍用語咁<br />\n由於佢哋冇腦<br />\n見到係親身經歷仲會信到十足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實開個account好易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以了解吓藍屍、建制嘅心態<br />\n又可以分化佢哋<br />\n一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲唔快啲做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2a1c858712ca90be49354954520bbaf9750acc","tid":1978620,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T22:42:00.000Z","msg":"問題係<br />\n人地Full time玩facebook<br />\n邊有時間做espionage ?"},{"pid":"2f703efb021148a179114cfe1be996d321291052","tid":1978620,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T22:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da7351a9688bfb0fb3b746b3572a17ddbfa7cfc","tid":1978620,"uid":228945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T22:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e264a64d921f86cc6c719016e13d5cc5eb64a9","tid":1978620,"uid":228945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T22:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa481e04d281b7fa2a72c329fa86d231fabd797","tid":1978620,"uid":95588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T22:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8fc29d97cc3b8cf7f6b07675fabc2d50e36efc6","tid":1978620,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T23:17:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02d65427009c10676fd73d572e9ce761d20142df","tid":1978620,"uid":80389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T01:10:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3a21267ddc80749be134528a60e652835bed6f6","tid":1978620,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T01:25:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc6b7f517925bd726ce84ad9ae69a87442a8ea0","tid":1978620,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:03:07.000Z","msg":"follow可以<br />\n唔應該like<br />\n黃圈不嬲like親建制page都會unfriend<br />\n雖然分身係無呢個問題<br />\n但唔想壯他人士氣"}]}